# CLAUDE.md — Dev VM Project Template

Copy this file to `/mnt/data/projects/<your-project>/CLAUDE.md` and customize for each project.

---

## Environment

This project runs on an Azure Ubuntu dev VM.

- **OS:** Ubuntu Pro 24.04 LTS
- **VM:** Standard_D16s_v5 (16 vCPU / 64 GB RAM)
- **Docker:** Available (Docker CE + Compose). Use `docker compose` (not `docker-compose`).
- **Disk layout:**
  - `/` — 30 GB OS disk (don't store project files here)
  - `/mnt/data/` — 512 GB Premium SSD (all projects, Docker volumes, data)

## Working directories

- **Projects:** `/mnt/data/projects/`
- **Docker volumes:** `/mnt/data/docker-volumes/`
- **OpenEMR:** `/mnt/data/openemr/`

## Conventions

- All services run as Docker containers. Prefer `docker compose` over installing runtimes directly on the host.
- Use `/mnt/data/docker-volumes/` for persistent database storage, not Docker anonymous volumes.
- The VM auto-shuts down at 8 PM UTC daily. Running containers will be stopped. Use `restart: unless-stopped` in compose files for services that should auto-resume.

## Infrastructure repo

The VM's Bicep template and setup scripts live in the `acto-infra` repo:
https://github.com/ACTO-LLC/acto-infra/tree/main/azure-dev-vm
